{"word":"σκυλακεύω","slug":"σκυλακεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκυλακεύω</b></el> <el>(σκῠλᾰκεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκύλαξ'><el>σκύλαξ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to pair dogs for breeding</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be suckled</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}